    dc:description "FIG. 6. — Traumatomutilla chuza Casal, 1969, male, French Guiana, Cayenne, INPA: A, lateral habitus; B-F, genitalia; B, dorsal view (halved); C, ventral view (halved); D, lateral/inner view (penis valve removed); E, cuspis, lateral/inner view (removed not to scale); F, penis valve, lateral/outer view (removed, not to scale). Scale bars: A, 2 mm. Photos: P. R. Bartholomay." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4450629/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4450635>
    dc:description "FIG. 8. — Traumatomutilla diopthalma (Klug, 1821), male, Pará, Serra Norte, MPEG: A, lateral habitus; B-F, genitalia: B, dorsal view (halved); C, ventral view (halved); D, lateral/inner view (penis valve removed); E, cuspis, lateral/inner view (removed not to scale); F, penis valve, lateral/outer view (removed, not to scale). Scale bar: 2 mm. Photos: P. R. Bartholomay." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4450635/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4450641>
    dc:description "FIG. 11. — Traumatomutilla gemella (André,1906),male,Brazil,Sao Paulo,EMUS:A, lateral habitus;B-F; genitalia:B, dorsal view (halved);C, ventral view (halved); D, lateral/inner view (penis valve removed); E, cuspis, lateral/inner view (removed not to scale); F, Penis valve, lateral/outer view (removed, not to scale). Scale bar: 2 mm. Photos: K. A. Williams." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4450641/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4450645>
    dc:description "FIG. 13. — Traumatomutilla peismatara Barholomay & Cambra n. sp., male,paratype,Brazil, Acre,Senador Guiomard,INPA:B-F, genitalia; B, dorsal view (halved); C, ventral view (halved); D, lateral/inner view (penis valve removed); E, cuspis, lateral/inner view (removed not to scale); F, penis valve,lateral/outer view (removed, not to scale). Scale bar: 2 mm. Photos: P. R. Bartholomay." ;
